00:14:30.376 --> 00:14:32.718
SP: A posse de armas nucleares.

00:14:32.718 --> 00:14:35.095
RNG: O apelo à religião para justificar

00:14:35.095 --> 00:14:36.735
o que seria injustificável,

00:14:36.735 --> 00:14:39.247
